    /* ─── Public stats (#75) — lives INSIDE the poster island, so it's a bespoke
         visual built from the poster's local palette. Aggregates only; no shared
         primitives reach in. Charts are CSS bars (no SVG, no JS) — the only inline
         style is a per-bar `--h`/`--w` ratio; all color/shape lives here. ─── */
    .stats { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .stats-intro { margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
